<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
  <title>DHOAS Application for a subsidy certificate | MyService</title>
  <% include ../../../../partials/head.ejs %>
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
  <noscript>
    <p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
  </noscript>
  <nav class="uikit-skip-link">
    <a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
  </nav>
  <% include ../../../../partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
  <% include ../../../../partials/header-nom-rep.ejs %>

  <main id="main-content">
    <div class="section-feature border-bottom--mild margin-above--none margin-below--none padding-below">
      <div class="container margin-above--none">
        <h1 class="margin-above--none ss-align--center">
          <span class="heading">Lump sum payment option</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 col-lg-offset-2 col-lg-8 margin-above--extra margin-below--extra">

          <p>Your entitlements will be paid monthly. You can choose to convert these payments into a single lump sum payment.</p>

          <div class="uikit-page-alerts" role="alert">
            <p>A request for the lump sum should be made on this application, however the assessment of your lump sum eligibility is made at payment commencement time after you confirm
              your request on the <a href="https://www.dhoas.gov.au/subsidy_authorisation_request" rel="external" target="_blank">Subsidy Authorisation Request Form (SARF)</a>
            </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  You must request the lump sum before you purchase or complete building your home.
                </li>
                <li>
                  The lump sum can only be paid on the Subsidy Certificate you requested before your home was purchased or completed.
                </li>
                <li>
                  If that Subsidy Certificate expires, and you are required to request a new Certificate after the home is purchased or completed, you will not be eligible for a lump
                  sum.
                </li>
              </ul>
          </div>

          <%- include(partials+"form_partials.ejs", {
            "forms": [
              {
                "type": "y_n_toggle",
                "config": {
                  "label": "Would you like to you check your eligibility for a lump sum payment?",
                  "yes_toggle": "#check-eligibility--yes",
                  "no_toggle": "#check-eligibility--no"
                }
              }
            ]
          }); %>

          <div id="check-eligibility--no" hidden>
            <p>Choose <b>save and next</b> to continue.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="check-eligibility--yes" hidden>
            <div id="eligibility-check">
              <%- include(partials+"form_partials.ejs", {
                "forms": [
                  {
                    "type": "y_n_toggle",
                    "config": {
                      "id": "serving-in-adf",
                      "label": "While serving in the ADF have you, or you and your partner, previously owned a 50% or greater stake in a home, either to live in or for an investment?"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }); %>

              <%- include(partials+"form_partials.ejs", {
                "forms": [
                  {
                    "type": "y_n_toggle",
                    "config": {
                      "id": "leave-within-12",
                      "label": "Do you expect to leave the ADF within 12 months of your subsidy payment being authorised?"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }); %>
            </div>

            <div id="may-be-eligible" hidden>
              <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--success">
                <p>You may be eligible to receive a lump sum payment.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                <p><strong>Important things to know:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                  <li>The maximum lump sum amount cannot exceed 48 months of payments.</li>
                  <li>Your monthly DHOAS payments may cease if you transfer to the Reserves and have less than 12 months of entitlement remaining after your lump sum payment is received.</li>
                  <li>You can find out more about DHOAS lump sum payments on the
                    <a href="http://dhoas.gov.au/8.-lump-sum.html" rel="external" target="_blank">DHOAS website</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <%- include(partials+"form_partials.ejs", {
                "forms": [
                  {
                    "type": "radio",
                    "config": {
                      "label": "How much of your entitlement do you want to receive as a lump sum?",
                      "hint": "You can choose how many months of your entitlement you would like to convert into a single lump sum payment.",
                      "boxes": [
                        {
                          "text": "Request the maximum amount"
                        },
                        {
                          "text": "Request a specific number of months",
                          "inject": "#specific-months-sum"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }); %>
        
              <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--error">
                <p><strong>You must agree with the following before your lump sum payment request can be submitted:</strong></p>
                <p>I acknowledge that the Scheme Administrator or the Department of Defence may recover an amount equal to my lump sum subsidy payment if I cease to be a member of the ADF within 12 months after payment is authorised.</p>
                <p>I also agree that my eligibility for the lump sum payment will be reassessed at payment commencement time.</p>
              </div>

            </div>

            <div id="not-eligible" hidden>
              <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--warning">
                <p>You are not eligible to receive a lump sum payment.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

            <%- include(partials+"form_partials.ejs", {"forms": [    {
                "type": "pagination",
                "config": {
                  "normal": [
                    {
                      "link": "/auth/claim/",
                      "primary": false,
                      "text": "Previous",
                    },
                    {
                      "link": "#open-modal",
                      "primary": false,
                      "text": "Cancel application",
                    }
                  ],
                  "floated": [
                    {
                      "link": "/auth/claim/",
                      "text": "Save and exit",
                      "primary": false,
                      "disabled": false
                    },
                    {
                      "link": "/auth/claim/dhoas/asc5",
                      "text": "Save and next",
                      "primary": true,
                      "disabled": false
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }]}) %>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <% include ../../../../partials/footer.ejs %>

<div id="specific-months-sum" class="form-group form-group--secondary" hidden>
  <span class="input-support-text">
    <span class="hint">I would like to convert &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>
  </span>
  <input type="number" class="uikit-text-input input-small mm">
  <span class="input-support-text">
    <span class="hint">&nbsp; months into a lump sum payment.</span>
  </span>
</div>

  <script>

    var adf_checked = false;
    var leave_checked = false;

    $("#serving-in-adf").on("click", "input", () => {
      if ($("#serving-in-adf-yes").prop("checked") || $("#serving-in-adf-no").prop("checked")) {
        adf_checked = true;
      }
    });

    $("#leave-within-12").on("click", "input", () => {
      if ($("#leave-within-12-yes").prop("checked") || $("#leave-within-12-no").prop("checked")) {
        leave_checked = true;
      }
    });

    $("#eligibility-check").on("click", "input", () => {
      if (adf_checked && leave_checked) {
        if($("#leave-within-12-no").prop("checked") && $("#serving-in-adf-no").prop("checked")) {
          $("#may-be-eligible").show();
          $("#not-eligible").hide();
        } else {
          $("#not-eligible").show();
          $("#may-be-eligible").hide();
        }
      }
    });

  </script>



</body>

</html>